<item>
            <title>[SEC-2219] OpenId Attribute Exchange does not work with Intuit Provider</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-2219</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;org.springframework.security.openidOpenID4JavaConsumer::fetchAxAttributes() uses the attribute name to retrieve the attribute values( List&amp;lt;String&amp;gt; values = fetchResp.getAttributeValues(attr.getName())&lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/images/icons/emoticons/wink.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;.  However, the intuit OP (which maybe a .NET provider) uses an alias scheme (not the attribute name) to provide values.  Partial responses from intuit OP (notice &quot;email&quot; attributes value is names value.alias3 (not &quot;email&quot;) :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;amp;openid.ns.alias3=&lt;a href=&quot;http://openid.net/srv/ax/1.0&amp;amp;openid.alias3.mode=fetch_response&amp;amp;openid.alias3.type.alias1=http://axschema.org/namePerson/first&amp;amp;openid.alias3.value.alias1=First&amp;amp;openid.alias3.type.alias2=http://axschema.org/namePerson/last&amp;amp;openid.alias3.value.alias2=Last&amp;amp;openid.alias3.type.alias3=http://axschema.org/contact/email&amp;amp;openid.alias3.value.alias3=noreply@psiflow.com&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://openid.net/srv/ax/1.0&amp;amp;openid.alias3.mode=fetch_response&amp;amp;openid.alias3.type.alias1=http://axschema.org/namePerson/first&amp;amp;openid.alias3.value.alias1=First&amp;amp;openid.alias3.type.alias2=http://axschema.org/namePerson/last&amp;amp;openid.alias3.value.alias2=Last&amp;amp;openid.alias3.type.alias3=http://axschema.org/contact/email&amp;amp;openid.alias3.value.alias3=noreply@psiflow.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;I believe the correct fix is to lookup attributes by type ( org.openid4java.message.ax.AxPayload::getAttributeValuesByTypeUri(String typeUri)) - however, I&apos;m a newbie to openid and admittedly don&apos;t know all the compatibility issues.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;security configuration for intuit OP:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;								&amp;lt;b:entry key=&quot;.&lt;b&gt;intuit.com.&lt;/b&gt;&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
									&amp;lt;b:list&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
										&amp;lt;b:bean class=&quot;org.springframework.security.openid.OpenIDAttribute&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
											&amp;lt;b:constructor-arg name=&quot;name&quot; value=&quot;email&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
											&amp;lt;b:constructor-arg name=&quot;type&quot; value=&quot;http://axschema.org/contact/email&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
											&amp;lt;b:property name=&quot;required&quot; value=&quot;true&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
										&amp;lt;/b:bean&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
										&amp;lt;b:bean class=&quot;org.springframework.security.openid.OpenIDAttribute&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
											&amp;lt;b:constructor-arg name=&quot;name&quot; value=&quot;firstname&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
											&amp;lt;b:constructor-arg name=&quot;type&quot; value=&quot;http://axschema.org/namePerson/first&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
											&amp;lt;b:property name=&quot;required&quot; value=&quot;true&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
										&amp;lt;/b:bean&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
										&amp;lt;b:bean class=&quot;org.springframework.security.openid.OpenIDAttribute&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
											&amp;lt;b:constructor-arg name=&quot;name&quot; value=&quot;lastname&quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
											&amp;lt;b:constructor-arg name=&quot;type&quot; value=&quot;http://axschema.org/namePerson/last&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
											&amp;lt;b:property name=&quot;required&quot; value=&quot;true&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
										&amp;lt;/b:bean&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
										&amp;lt;b:bean class=&quot;org.springframework.security.openid.OpenIDAttribute&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
											&amp;lt;b:constructor-arg name=&quot;name&quot; value=&quot;realmId&quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
											&amp;lt;b:constructor-arg name=&quot;type&quot; value=&quot;http://axschema.org/intuit/realmId&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
											&amp;lt;b:property name=&quot;required&quot; value=&quot;true&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
										&amp;lt;/b:bean&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
									&amp;lt;/b:list&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
